{"tid":700141,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[踩遊記] 以色列 · 巴勒斯坦","createTime":"2018-06-13T06:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T08:12:18.000Z","uid":59197,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"17484b632f201c074a9c80c232e1cc82da0f1d81","tid":700141,"uid":59197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"開始前戴個頭盔先 &mdash; 關於以巴衝突，個人認為政治無中立，係人都有立場，我都有嘅。不論你係反阿拉伯反穆斯林定反美帝盟友，都希望大家抱住輕鬆心情睇。本人無宗教信仰，但好鍾意睇宗教嘢。閒時寫下旅途見聞，盡量做足功課先講，如果有錯希望各位巴絲屌細力啲，多多指教。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n自從三年前去完伊朗之後，一直都好想去埋以色列同巴勒斯坦。上年，即係2017年，猶太新年Rosh Hashanah 係九月尾，適逢我嘅英國working holiday visa九月中到期，咁就決定由倫敦飛去以色列留一個月，再由以色列返香港。<br />\n<br />\n中間呢一個月，我用couchsurfing嘅形式去咗以色列嘅Jerusalem, Haifa, Nazareth, Acre, Caesarea, En Gedi, Masada, Dead Sea同巴勒斯坦嘅Ramallah, Bethlehem, Nablus同佢附近嘅Balata Refugee Camp。<br />\n<br />\n本來打算去過猶太新年，搭單行下巴勒斯坦。最後竟然喺巴勒斯坦留得耐過以色列，睇到以色列年輕一代反戰嘅爭扎、巴勒斯坦嘅凋零，見咗好多唔同背景嘅人，包括阿拉伯裔以色列人、仇穆嘅猶太家庭、生到一竇都係嘅傳統阿拉伯家庭、世俗化嘅穆斯林等等，親身感受以巴衝突。最重要係終於唔係透過書同網絡，而係第一身聽以色列人同巴勒斯坦人點講呢兩個地方。<br />\n以色列同巴勒斯坦雖只一牆之隔，但唔少兩地居民永世未踏入過自己嘅「另一半國土」。而我一個外國人，竟然可以自由進出兩地，踩入聖地範圍。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n由倫敦去Tel Aviv可以坐 Easyjet / Monarch，兩間都係廉航，價錢都差唔多。今次我坐Easyjet，大約五個鐘，機票百零鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/123000_36360657f304b47fcbc76cb9cba2845f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F123000_36360657f304b47fcbc76cb9cba2845f.png&h=2aa0f3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/123005_6c2d85f487b8b6bf3b818105d999c00b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F123005_6c2d85f487b8b6bf3b818105d999c00b.png&h=f9b384e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以色列入境排咗好耐，同傳聞一樣的確係問長問短，同英國差唔多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/123009_d94690a9fb1d6ac3c178b9ccc960e7ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F123009_d94690a9fb1d6ac3c178b9ccc960e7ef.png&h=1f135ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n​<br />\n好多人關心嘅護照問題 &mdash; 特區同BNO去以色列都免簽。由於我當年用特區護照去伊朗，考慮到有伊朗簽證可能入唔到境，於是我用BNO入以色列。另一個經常有人問嘅問題，護照有以色列印會唔會令你去唔到其他地方？Tel Aviv機場嘅話會俾一張entry card你，上面有個QR code俾你入閘入境（之後入巴勒斯坦都需要睇下呢張紙仔）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/123012_c8a41d58bad2442bda29c34952b6e86a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F123012_c8a41d58bad2442bda29c34952b6e86a.png&h=1b65e5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我用BNO去英國working holiday，去歐洲旅行除咗愛爾蘭全部都唔會吸印。所以我本BNO上只有一堆英國入境印，令佢無乜關於去過邊到嘅問題問我，只係問咗以下呢堆循例問題：<br />\n嚟幾耐？一個月。<br />\n嚟做咩？過猶太新年。<br />\n咁耐？除咗Rosh Hashana仲有Yom Kippur同Sukkot啊（後兩個都係重要猶太節日，都係同一個月）。<br />\n你係Jewish？唔係，但我嘅猶太朋友話呢幾個節日對猶太人好重要，希望我可以嚟以色列感受。<br />\n住邊？朋友屋企。<br />\n地址？無，因為佢嚟接我。<br />\n然後我主動俾回程機票佢睇，張機票係我位以色列妹朋友訂，見到電郵有希伯來文佢就放行。<br />\n總結入境比我想像中容易得多，反而離境時問得仲多問題。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nShalom!<br />\n<br />\n入咗境拎埋個蝸牛殼，我就搵巴士向我第一個目的地－耶路撒冷進發。"},{"pid":"7f44eac8ddb6503399fbcd1a7daac89ffc7d652c","tid":700141,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"樓主擔唔擔心安全問題?"},{"pid":"b748504d1177c47a86082c1e6ef705a5b25869bd","tid":700141,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8ed1acffe5031ea07495cac48ed9336b7c46d9","tid":700141,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbb496c121b873da24f9229c84137cd5aff9cce","tid":700141,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28381e3ed039391e8b8df1198f1f20d2f6c76a8a","tid":700141,"uid":71008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"🧐🧐🧐🧐🧐🧐🧐🧐"},{"pid":"b6a83134d976db24c0d91fe66b7973b61f336a48","tid":700141,"uid":80045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺以色列返嚟<br />\nLm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864e6a91b17de8cf7382879e7a5c5e1fa2e24b1e","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"有israel 入境印都可以同一本PASSPORT入巴嗎?"},{"pid":"a2bf5965ffa77410436ee52f460ebae8f11f729a","tid":700141,"uid":81309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"788ceba032acc5046bfc9ad13e39dba8a8d08d80","tid":700141,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"深度遊，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0992bf6ebc85e0bd624122dc77caac8d23d1023","tid":700141,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"踩你返黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbe26f9afa3007044f429ff05ef9cc9695ce393","tid":700141,"uid":84697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3de0dc88e81ebda63ea59e8fe6ca99213309e6","tid":700141,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"終於出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29a1d99ade74289b90659b0f4feb25c60374253","tid":700141,"uid":59197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103629_9adc11780ac706fe1799d8de1af01c8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103629_9adc11780ac706fe1799d8de1af01c8a.png&h=6461b1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由Tel Aviv去Jerusalem巴士車程一個鐘多啲，落車就等我嘅host嚟接我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103627_386955cf9388a3302a15850b1d83511b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103627_386955cf9388a3302a15850b1d83511b.png&h=a826fcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺呢個有啲up dup嘅路邊見到有架audi停低都幾格格不入。<br />\n<br />\n然後一個非常西化嘅阿拉伯人落車同我握手。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Welcome to the Holy Land.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以巴之行第一個Host Nabil，一個阿拉伯裔以色列人。<br />\n<br />\n以色列建國當年，好多巴勒斯坦人被驅逐到West Bank, Gaza範圍或其他中東國家如敍利亞/埃及/黎巴嫩等。佢鄉下係以色列北面一個小城，咁啱當年避過一劫，無俾以色列軍隊驅離家園，家族得以繼續喺到生活。於是佢生於阿拉伯家庭，但喺以色列出世，擁有以色列護照。<br />\n<br />\n以巴戰爭，以色列同巴勒斯坦背後係美國同沙地、伊朗等中東國家組成嘅阿拉伯聯盟嘅角力。即使Nabil係阿拉伯人，但因為佢揸以色列護照，中東只有三個阿拉伯國家佢可以去&mdash;約旦、埃及、摩洛哥。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It's not about religions. It's politics.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n「你可以話我係以色列人，但我無選擇以色列人呢個身份，只係我喺呢到出世，我拎呢本護照。我唔係巴勒斯坦人，我認同以色列係我嘅國家，但我唔會否定我嘅阿拉伯血統、文化。我只係想好好喺到生活。我係阿拉伯人，我於阿拉伯文化中長大，我講寫阿位伯文。我愛阿拉伯古典音樂，希望令更多人認識到。」<br />\n<br />\n如果喺Palestinian Territory, 巴勒斯坦自治區範圍即West Bank, Gaza地區內出世，先可以申請巴勒斯坦護照，無得話喺以色列出世但要求入巴勒斯坦籍。但其實唔係一個身份證明文件，只係旅遊證件。根本無巴勒斯坦呢個國籍，無香港呢個國籍。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nNabil係一位音樂家，讀緊Musicology PhD，同時又係Hebrew University of Jerusalem 嘅East Arabian Music 大學教授，住喺大學嘅學生宿舍。一個非常西化嘅阿拉伯人，喺耶路撒冷最出名嘅大學教傳統阿拉伯樂，好有趣。<br />\n<br />\n佢擅長嘅樂器係一種叫OUD嘅傳統阿拉伯樂器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ethnicmusical.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/turkish-oud-mustafa-kamil-rosewood-1-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ethnicmusical.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fturkish-oud-mustafa-kamil-rosewood-1-2.jpg&h=a97a536c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有啲似結他。<br />\n<br />\n雖然專長係音樂，但佢對體育、語言、宗教、歷史都好有認識。條友玩越野單車，除咗阿拉伯文希伯來文又識法文德文，住喺耶路撒冷嘅佢對於聖城歷史倒背如流。以為係阿拉伯人就係穆斯林？錯了，佢係天主教徒&hellip;但對猶太教同伊斯蘭教嘅認識都唔少。玩晒啦。<br />\n<br />\n於是，我日日都捉住佢問勁多問題&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n講漏咗，呢條友仔好崇拜李小龍，目標係做到佢嘅二指掌上壓。<br />\n早排佢send咗段片俾我，已經練到三隻手指。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n​"},{"pid":"cceb673d299e964ccd2e8f4f86270550eef601fe","tid":700141,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce1d9b807761a6c9baaa76f0e9e48246a175193","tid":700141,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"864e6a91b17de8cf7382879e7a5c5e1fa2e24b1e","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"有israel 入境印都可以同一本PASSPORT入巴嗎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦唔係國家嚟架。<br />\n<br />\n以色列過去無檢查，調番轉就有<br />\n<br />\n巴人唔係話過就過得以色列，好多去到檢查站就俾人捉落車。<br />\n<br />\n同埋樓主咪講咗囉，得張入境紙，唔會留任何印喺你本PASSPORT度。"},{"pid":"730122a59c65c605a3487f6cbde4d5fd4154fd55","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce1d9b807761a6c9baaa76f0e9e48246a175193","tid":700141,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"864e6a91b17de8cf7382879e7a5c5e1fa2e24b1e","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"有israel 入境印都可以同一本PASSPORT入巴嗎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦唔係國家嚟架。<br />\n<br />\n以色列過去無檢查，調番轉就有<br />\n<br />\n巴人唔係話過就過得以色列，好多去到檢查站就俾人捉落車。<br />\n<br />\n同埋樓主咪講咗囉，得張入境紙，唔會留任何印喺你本PASSPORT度。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"明白 thx"},{"pid":"06aa2cd89bf893e6a802e066bf17b1565c2a4141","tid":700141,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"730122a59c65c605a3487f6cbde4d5fd4154fd55","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce1d9b807761a6c9baaa76f0e9e48246a175193","tid":700141,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"864e6a91b17de8cf7382879e7a5c5e1fa2e24b1e","tid":700141,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"有israel 入境印都可以同一本PASSPORT入巴嗎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦唔係國家嚟架。<br />\n<br />\n以色列過去無檢查，調番轉就有<br />\n<br />\n巴人唔係話過就過得以色列，好多去到檢查站就俾人捉落車。<br />\n<br />\n同埋樓主咪講咗囉，得張入境紙，唔會留任何印喺你本PASSPORT度。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"明白 thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"不過有人講過如果你以色列陸路過埃及<br />\n<br />\n埃及嗰邊個幫你蓋佢個入境印落你本 PASSPORT  (聽聞約旦就無)<br />\n<br />\n咁你本PASSPORT 準備拎唔到伊朗 VISA ，同埋你去回教國家都可能有問題。<br />\n<br />\n人哋一睇你個印就知你去過以色列。<br />\n<br />\n等於人哋見到本護照有個中国羅湖口岸印，就知你去過香港一樣。"},{"pid":"653c88c6924b9a36702897861556fb2472af9a79","tid":700141,"uid":50537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"b436378eba70da7c7f1127293395b23afd0b8f74","tid":700141,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"LM爛尾"},{"pid":"8f93d1a14839acbce510caf22c65c1efb73adcbd","tid":700141,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c4148ffc88a15674861e1adf4382db6642b6dc","tid":700141,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"捨得出未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9363fb8c685acb5697d34f91b5e767f3fb53a041","tid":700141,"uid":59197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"去到宿舍放低行李出去搵嘢食。第一樣就係食中東最出名嘅falefel。以色列人會話falefel係以色列傳純食物。但老實說以色列立國不久，食物文化等都係由附近中東國家引入。Falefel 源自埃及，中東各個地方整法稍稍不同。大致上都係ground chicken peas &amp; fava beans打碎造成粉團再炸成波波，可以就咁做，或者放入包到再配大量青瓜酸菜洋蔥五顏六色菜等等。我就麻麻地，但佢係最出名嘅中東小食。<br />\n<br />\nSorry我張圖見唔到啲炸波波，喺晒底。<br />\n​<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103630_1643eb60071ad3b7c288f066911d79c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103630_1643eb60071ad3b7c288f066911d79c0.png&h=8d521d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完Falefel我已經收皮，直接瞓到第二日下晝。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n上面講到Nabil係大學教授，所以佢早早出去上lecture。下晝落堂返嚟煮咗佢家鄉嘅食物我食。咪睇佢咁肉酸，其實好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，係炒香嘅洋蔥撈埋豆同米再配包。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103631_2e19a8bf96bc96159bc7ae26f40dae70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103631_2e19a8bf96bc96159bc7ae26f40dae70.png&h=c43c961b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飯後來一杯極濃中東咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103631_f97a3829999ee852f4ec2f4ba2eeb18c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103631_f97a3829999ee852f4ec2f4ba2eeb18c.png&h=177870eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n耶路撒冷市內主要交通工具係巴士同輕鐵。輕鐵車費唔係計距離，搭幾遠一程都係同一價錢，一次過買多幾程都無平。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/103633_046fae807ba130f9c1fa67cec7fc4f93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F103633_046fae807ba130f9c1fa67cec7fc4f93.png&h=978559ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n​<br />\n大西北出身嘅小人，唔需要好似其他遊客一面茫然，輕鬆駕馭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n​"},{"pid":"09de124e810923f14a3e61c0b4708495d69985f6","tid":700141,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a5f39b8b1a35b352681e59c1d2805a0ce3c703","tid":700141,"uid":69071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"留名。本身想去，但機票太貴，唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}